sentences.sentence: Compared with males, the effect of CF was more pronounced in female fasters.
sentences.translation: 与男性相比，女性禁食者表现得更为明显。

sentences.sentence: He has had several death threats. Only a handful of Moroccans, such as the editors of the country's first gay magazine (published for the time being in Spain), have backed the non-fasters.
sentences.translation: 他甚至已经接收到了一些死亡威胁。目前，只有少部份摩洛哥人，其中包括该国第一家同性恋杂志(在西班牙时出版过)的编辑表示支持非斋戒人士。
